<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Route Optimization — Evaluasi Rute Mantri</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="vendor/leaflet.css"/>
<script src="vendor/leaflet.js"></script>
<script src="vendor/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
:root{
  --ink:#0a1a2f; --paper:#f5f2ec; --card:#ffffff;
  --navy:#13335c; --navy2:#1d4d87; --sky:#3b82c4;
  --amber:#e8a13a; --amber-d:#c47e1c; --rust:#b3492d;
  --teal:#1f8a78; --line:#dcd6ca; --muted:#5b6675;
  --good:#1f8a78; --bad:#b3492d;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;line-height:1.5}
.wrap{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px}
.mono{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
h1,h2,h3{font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;letter-spacing:-.02em}

/* HERO */
header{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0a1a2f 0%,#13335c 55%,#1d4d87 100%);color:#fff;padding:46px 0 130px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
header::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px,rgba(255,255,255,.10) 1px,transparent 0);background-size:26px 26px;opacity:.5}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;font-family:'Sora';font-weight:700;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9ec3e6;position:relative;z-index:1}
.brand .dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--amber)}
.hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.3fr 1fr;gap:40px;align-items:end;margin-top:30px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.eyebrow{font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--amber);margin-bottom:14px}
h1{font-size:clamp(30px,4.4vw,52px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.04}
h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--amber);position:relative}
.lede{color:#c8d8ea;font-size:16px;margin-top:18px;max-width:46ch}
.hero-stat{text-align:right}
.hero-stat .big{font-family:'Sora';font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(56px,9vw,104px);line-height:.9;color:#fff}
.hero-stat .big span{color:var(--amber)}
.hero-stat .cap{font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-size:13px;color:#9ec3e6;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-top:8px}

/* KPI STRIP */
.kpis{margin-top:-88px;position:relative;z-index:3;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px}
.kpi{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:20px 18px;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(10,26,47,.10)}
.kpi .lbl{font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
.kpi .val{font-family:'Sora';font-weight:800;font-size:30px;margin-top:8px;color:var(--navy)}
.kpi .val small{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted)}
.kpi .sub{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:5px}

/* SECTIONS */
section{padding:54px 0}
.sec-head{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:16px;margin-bottom:8px}
.sec-num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-size:13px;color:var(--amber-d);font-weight:600}
h2{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy)}
.sec-sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:15px;margin:6px 0 28px;max-width:64ch}

.panel{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;padding:24px}
.cols{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
.cols-3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr;gap:20px}
.chart-box{position:relative;height:320px}
.panel h3{font-size:16px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:4px}
.panel .ph{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px}

/* MAP */
#map{height:440px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--line)}
.legend{display:flex;gap:20px;margin-top:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.legend span{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink);font-weight:500}
.swatch{width:22px;height:4px;border-radius:2px}
.map-stat{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-top:14px}
.map-stat div{flex:1;background:var(--paper);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid var(--line)}
.map-stat .n{font-family:'Sora';font-weight:800;font-size:22px;color:var(--navy)}
.map-stat .l{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'JetBrains Mono';letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}

/* TABLE */
.tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13.5px}
.tbl th{text-align:left;font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);padding:11px 12px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--line)}
.tbl td{padding:11px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.tbl tr:hover td{background:#faf8f3}
.tbl .num{text-align:right;font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-weight:500}
.tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px}
.bar{height:6px;border-radius:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--rust),var(--amber))}
.barcell{min-width:90px}
.toolbar{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.toolbar button{font-family:'Inter';font-size:13px;font-weight:600;padding:7px 14px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff;border-radius:20px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted);transition:.15s}
.toolbar button.active{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;border-color:var(--navy)}
.toolbar button:hover{border-color:var(--navy2)}

/* ALGO */
.steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;margin-top:8px}
.step{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:20px;position:relative}
.step .k{font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-size:12px;color:var(--amber-d);font-weight:600}
.step h4{font-family:'Sora';font-size:15px;margin:10px 0 7px;color:var(--navy)}
.step p{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
.codeblock{background:#0a1a2f;color:#cfe0f0;border-radius:14px;padding:22px 24px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono';font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.7;overflow-x:auto;margin-top:20px}
.codeblock .c{color:#6a8aae}
.codeblock .k{color:var(--amber)}
.codeblock .s{color:#7fcab5}

.callout{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#13335c,#1d4d87);color:#fff;border-radius:16px;padding:30px 32px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:14px}
.callout div .n{font-family:'Sora';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;color:var(--amber)}
.callout div .l{font-size:13px;color:#c8d8ea;margin-top:4px}

footer{padding:34px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;text-align:center}
@media(max-width:880px){
  .hero-grid,.cols,.cols-3{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .kpis{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .steps{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .callout{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .hero-stat{text-align:left}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="brand"><span class="dot"></span> BRI · Micro Risk Analytics</div>
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Route Optimization · Pemasaran · Pembinaan · Penagihan</div>
        <h1>Setiap kilometer rute mantri<br>adalah <em>biaya & waktu</em><br>yang bisa dipangkas.</h1>
        <p class="lede">Evaluasi rute aktual mantri lapangan dan model optimalisasi berbasis data GPS kunjungan harian.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="big"><span id="h-save">55</span>%</div>
        <div class="cap">rata-rata jarak rute<br>dapat dipangkas</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="wrap">
  <div class="kpis" id="kpis"></div>
</div>

<!-- 1. EVALUASI -->
<section class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head"><span class="sec-num">01</span><h2>Evaluasi rute penagihan saat ini</h2></div>
  <p class="sec-sub">Rute aktual direkonstruksi dari urutan waktu kunjungan (jam_kunjungan) per mantri per hari. Jarak dihitung dengan formula haversine antar titik berurutan, lalu dibandingkan dengan rute optimal sebagai benchmark.</p>
  <div class="cols-3">
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Jarak rute mingguan: aktual vs optimal</h3>
      <p class="ph">Rata-rata km per mantri-hari, dirata-ratakan per minggu</p>
      <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="trend"></canvas></div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Komposisi aktivitas kunjungan</h3>
      <p class="ph">Penagihan & pemasaran adalah beban rute terbesar</p>
      <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="donut"></canvas></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 2. PETA -->
<section class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head"><span class="sec-num">02</span><h2>Anatomi satu hari rute mantri</h2></div>
  <p class="sec-sub">Contoh nyata dari data: satu mantri, satu hari kerja. Garis merah adalah urutan kunjungan aktual (berdasar waktu), garis hijau adalah rute hasil optimalisasi terhadap titik yang sama.</p>
  <div class="panel">
    <div id="map"></div>
    <div class="legend">
      <span><span class="swatch" style="background:#b3492d"></span> Rute aktual (urutan waktu)</span>
      <span><span class="swatch" style="background:#1f8a78"></span> Rute optimal (model)</span>
      <span><span class="swatch" style="background:#13335c;width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%"></span> Titik kunjungan</span>
    </div>
    <div class="map-stat" id="mapstat"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 3. REGIONAL -->
<section class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head"><span class="sec-num">03</span><h2>Peringkat efisiensi per wilayah & unit kerja</h2></div>
  <p class="sec-sub">Semakin tinggi potensi penghematan, semakin tidak efisien pola rute saat ini — dan semakin besar dampak implementasi optimalisasi.</p>
  <div class="cols">
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Potensi penghematan per Kanwil</h3>
      <p class="ph">% jarak yang dapat dipangkas vs rata-rata km aktual/hari</p>
      <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="region"></canvas></div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Unit kerja prioritas</h3>
      <p class="ph">Unit dengan rute terpanjang & potensi penghematan tertinggi</p>
      <div class="toolbar" id="uktools">
        <button data-sort="saving" class="active">Penghematan %</button>
        <button data-sort="act">Km aktual</button>
        <button data-sort="avgn">Kunjungan/hari</button>
      </div>
      <div style="max-height:300px;overflow-y:auto">
        <table class="tbl" id="uktbl"><thead><tr>
          <th>Unit Kerja</th><th class="num">Aktual</th><th class="num">Optimal</th><th class="barcell">Hemat</th>
        </tr></thead><tbody></tbody></table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 4. ALGORITMA -->
<section class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head"><span class="sec-num">04</span><h2>Model optimalisasi rute</h2></div>
  <p class="sec-sub">Persoalan ini adalah varian Travelling Salesman Problem (TSP) berskala harian per mantri. Modelnya ringan, deterministik, dan bisa berjalan di perangkat lapangan tanpa server berat.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="k">STEP 01</div><h4>Ingest & cleaning</h4><p>Filter status DONE, buang koordinat di luar bounding-box Indonesia (GPS error), urutkan per mantri-hari.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="k">STEP 02</div><h4>Matriks jarak</h4><p>Haversine antar seluruh titik kunjungan. Dapat di-upgrade ke jarak jalan (OSRM) untuk akurasi rute nyata.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="k">STEP 03</div><h4>Nearest-Neighbor</h4><p>Konstruksi rute awal: dari titik awal, selalu pilih kunjungan terdekat yang belum dikunjungi.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="k">STEP 04</div><h4>2-opt refinement</h4><p>Tukar segmen rute selama masih memperpendek total jarak. Konvergen cepat untuk ≤40 titik/hari.</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="codeblock"><span class="c"># Inti model — Nearest-Neighbor + 2-opt (Python)</span>
<span class="k">def</span> optimize_route(lat, lon):
    order = nearest_neighbor(lat, lon, start=<span class="s">0</span>)   <span class="c"># rute greedy awal</span>
    order, km = two_opt(lat, lon, order)            <span class="c"># perbaikan lokal</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> order, km                             <span class="c"># urutan optimal + jarak (km)</span>

<span class="c"># 2-opt: balik segmen [i..k] jika total rute jadi lebih pendek</span>
<span class="k">def</span> two_opt(lat, lon, order):
    <span class="k">for</span> i <span class="k">in</span> range(<span class="s">1</span>, n-<span class="s">1</span>):
        <span class="k">for</span> k <span class="k">in</span> range(i+<span class="s">1</span>, n):
            new = order[:i] + order[i:k+<span class="s">1</span>][::-<span class="s">1</span>] + order[k+<span class="s">1</span>:]
            <span class="k">if</span> route_length(new) &lt; best_len: best = new</div>
</section>

<!-- 5. DAMPAK -->
<section class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head"><span class="sec-num">05</span><h2>Proyeksi dampak implementasi</h2></div>
  <p class="sec-sub">Diekstrapolasi dari penghematan jarak terukur pada seluruh mantri-hari dalam dataset.</p>
  <div class="callout" id="impact"></div>
  <p class="sec-sub" style="margin-top:22px">Penghematan jarak berarti lebih banyak debitur dapat dikunjungi per hari (kapasitas penagihan & pembinaan naik), BBM dan waktu tempuh turun, serta cakupan pembinaan nasabah baru meluas tanpa menambah headcount.</p>
</section>

<footer class="wrap">
  Dashboard analitik rute mantri · Dibangun dengan Python (pandas, NN+2-opt) · Leaflet · Chart.js<br>
  Dapat dipublikasikan gratis via GitHub Pages. Data agregat, tanpa identitas debitur.
</footer>

